{"word":"G2669 - καταπονέω - kataponéō - kat-ap-on-eh'-o - Oppress","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταπονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kataponéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ap-on-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Oppress</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துன்பப்படு, வருத்தப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to tire down with toil, exhaust with labor"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4192 - πόνος - pónos - pon'-os/4192\">G4192</a>; to <i>labor down</i>, that is, <i>wear with toil</i> (figuratively <i>harass</i>): - oppress, vex.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}